---
import '../styles/main.css';

---

<section class="h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-[#010105] via-[#010105]/20 to-[#010105]">
    <div class="py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl lg:py-16 lg:px-6">

        <!-- Header & Description Start -->
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-md text-center mb-8 lg:mb-12">
            <p class="text-lg font-sans text-teal-500"></p>
            <h2 class="mt-3 mb-4 text-3xl tracking-tight font-mono font-medium md:text-4xl text-white">Solving the Problems</h2>
            <p class="font-light font-sans sm:text-xl text-gray-400">I noticed that most of the competitors sites have reviews from clients about a job well done they did on their property. However, I put myself in the shoes of a new client and asked myself, "Can I see the job they done for that client?"</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Header & Description End -->

        <!-- Pricing Card Container Start -->
        <div class="space-y-8 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-6 xl:gap-10 lg:space-y-0">

            <slot name="problemCard"/>
            <slot name="solutionCard"/>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</section>